title: S4, Ep4: Lowkey Losin' It
itunes:author: Loud Speakers Network
itunes:summary:
Everything in Issa’s life seems to be going left lately — from the best laid of block party plans to literally trying to negotiate space with her bestie. Join Crissle and Fran as they talk about former flames, new parents and everything in between.

Don’t forget to join in on the conversation and follow along on social media with the hashtag #insecuriTEA

Executive Producers: Chris Morrow, Matt Raz
Producer: Matt Raz
Editor: Ty Worley
Engineer: Dwayne Crawford
